_sText: This is a short and sweet map i originally made for L4D, but reduced in size by a factor of 2 in order to create more close quarters battle. Terrorists have hijacked the HSwMS Härnösand and are threatening to execute hostages, most of whom are high ranking members of the royal swedish navy. Särskilda Skyddsgruppen operatives have infiltrated the vessel and are about to launch an assault!
